Manage MCPAccessGrant resources

Usage:
  mcp-runtime access grant [command]

Available Commands:
  apply       Apply a grant manifest
  delete      Delete an access grant
  disable     Disable a grant
  enable      Enable a grant
  get         Get an access grant
  list        List access grants

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for grant

Global Flags:
      --debug   Enable debug mode with structured error logging

Use "mcp-runtime access grant [command] --help" for more information about a command.
